snippet.title: Planetary Settlers Trailer April 2019
snippet.description:
This trailer for my game Planetary Settlers shows off some of the more interesting features and missions, and shows what it is all about!  Learn about the solar system as you play!  Check it out on Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/857860/Planetary_Settlers/

Check out the full Planetary Settlers development play list here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SD9wx7L1vVM&list=PL9Bk1v7iJfdCpRaQ6vTGYOM-lXAO7RAQ1

If you want to see my Second Life creations, including the Gospel Theater, check out this playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ykhXfCreQ5k&list=PL9Bk1v7iJfdDDw1dX9CkMfPWiB0AWQt62
